{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018qcbhpTvHZjgWodHgqJMSW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here's my comprehensive exploration report:\n\n## Game-Engine Package - Full Exploration Report\n\n### 1. **Directory Structure**\n\n```\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/\n├── src/\n│   ├── browser.ts                    (browser-safe exports)\n│   ├── coinflip.ts                   (coinflip game logic + PDAs)\n│   ├── GameEventEmitter.ts           (event system)\n│   ├── index.ts                      (main exports)\n│   ├── instructions.ts               (legacy instruction builders)\n│   ├── payouts.ts                    (payout calculations)\n│   ├── RoundStateMachine.ts          (round state management)\n│   └── types.ts                      (all type definitions + constants)\n├── eslint.config.js\n├── package.json\n├── tsconfig.json\n└── node_modules/\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. **package.json**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@rng-utopia/game-engine\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"main\": \"./src/index.ts\",\n  \"types\": \"./src/index.ts\",\n  \"exports\": {\n    \".\": \"./src/index.ts\",\n    \"./browser\": \"./src/browser.ts\"\n  },\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest --passWithNoTests\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@solana/web3.js\": \"^1.98.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@rng-utopia/config\": \"workspace:*\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^22.10.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.1.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. **tsconfig.json**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"@rng-utopia/config/tsconfig.base.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"types\": [\"node\"]\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src\"]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. **src/index.ts (Main Exports)**\n\nThe package exports:\n\n**Round State Machine:**\n- `RoundStateMachine`, `RoundState`, `RoundPhase`\n\n**Payout Calculations:**\n- `calculatePariMutuelPayout` (UI verification only)\n- `calculateWinnerPayout`\n- `verifyPayoutInvariant`\n\n**Event Emitter:**\n- `GameEventEmitter`, `GameEvent`, `GameEventType`\n\n**Legacy Instructions (deprecated):**\n- `buildEntryInstruction`, `buildCashoutInstruction`\n\n**Types:**\n- `Tier`, `Pool`, `PoolPhase`, `PlayerEntry`, `Side`, `GameConfig`, `GameId`\n- `CoinSide`, `CoinflipPhase`, `CoinflipState`, `CoinflipMatch`\n- `PoolState`, `LegacyPlayerEntry` (backwards compatibility)\n\n**Constants:**\n- `TIER_VALUES`, `TIER_AMOUNTS`, `POOL_PHASE_VALUES`, `SIDE_VALUES`\n- `COIN_SIDE_VALUES`, `COINFLIP_PHASE_VALUES`, `GAME_IDS`\n- `XP_BY_TIER`, `FEE_CONSTANTS`\n\n**Coinflip Game:**\n- `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID`, `PROGRAM_IDS` (deprecated)\n- `getMatchPda`, `getConfigPda`\n- `getEntryAmount`, `calculatePotentialPayout`\n- `getOppositeSide`, `determineWinnerFromRandomness`\n\n---\n\n### 5. **src/types.ts - Full Type Definitions & Constants**\n\n**Tier System:**\n```typescript\ntype Tier = \"iron\" | \"bronze\" | \"silver\" | \"gold\" | \"platinum\" | \"diamond\";\n\nconst TIER_VALUES: Record<Tier, number> = {\n  iron: 0, bronze: 1, silver: 2, gold: 3, platinum: 4, diamond: 5\n};\n\nconst TIER_AMOUNTS: Record<Tier, number> = {\n  iron: 0.005, bronze: 0.01, silver: 0.1, gold: 0.25, platinum: 0.5, diamond: 1.0\n};\n```\n\n**Pool State:**\n```typescript\ntype PoolPhase = \"waiting\" | \"locked\" | \"resolving\" | \"settled\" | \"cancelled\";\n\ninterface Pool {\n  poolId: Uint8Array;\n  gameId: string;\n  roundId: number;\n  tier: Tier;\n  entryAmount: number;\n  phase: PoolPhase;\n  totalPool: number;\n  playerCount: number;\n  maxPlayers: number;\n  createdAt: Date;\n  lockedAt: Date | null;\n  settledAt: Date | null;\n  feeBps: number;\n  vrfRequest: PublicKey | null;\n  randomness: Uint8Array | null;\n  winner: PublicKey | null;\n  authority: PublicKey;\n  treasury: PublicKey;\n  carryoverAmount: number;\n  carryoverFromRound: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Player Entry:**\n```typescript\ntype Side = \"none\" | \"green\" | \"red\";\n\ninterface PlayerEntry {\n  pool: PublicKey;\n  player: PublicKey;\n  amount: number;\n  enteredAt: Date;\n  sequence: number;\n  side: Side;\n  cashoutMultiplier: number | null;\n  cashedOutAt: Date | null;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  payout: number;\n  won: boolean;\n  xpParticipation: number;\n  xpWin: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Coinflip:**\n```typescript\ntype CoinSide = \"heads\" | \"tails\";\ntype CoinflipPhase = \"created\" | \"ready\" | \"flipping\" | \"complete\";\n\ninterface CoinflipState {\n  pool: PublicKey;\n  player1: PublicKey;\n  player2: PublicKey | null;\n  player1Side: CoinSide;\n  result: CoinSide | null;\n  phase: CoinflipPhase;\n  createdAt: Date;\n  joinedAt: Date | null;\n  flippedAt: Date | null;\n  joinTimeoutSecs: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Game IDs:**\n```typescript\nconst GAME_IDS = {\n  COINFLIP: \"coinflip\",\n  LORD_OF_RNGS: \"lord-of-rngs\",\n  CRASH: \"crash\",\n  CLOSE_CALL: \"close-call\",\n  SLOTS: \"slots\",\n  GAME_OF_TRADES: \"game-of-trades\",\n  TUG_OF_EARN: \"tug-of-earn\",\n  CHART_COURSE: \"chart-course\",\n};\n```\n\n**Fee Constants:**\n```typescript\nconst FEE_CONSTANTS = {\n  TOTAL_BPS: 300,              // 3%\n  PLATFORM_REVENUE_BPS: 200,   // 2.0%\n  RAKEBACK_POOL_BPS: 70,       // 0.7% — raid boss rewards\n  CHEST_TREASURY_BPS: 30,      // 0.3% — treasure chests\n};\n```\n\n**XP System:**\n```typescript\nconst XP_BY_TIER: Record<Tier, { participation: number; win: number }> = {\n  iron: { participation: 1, win: 3 },\n  bronze: { participation: 1, win: 3 },\n  silver: { participation: 10, win: 30 },\n  gold: { participation: 25, win: 75 },\n  platinum: { participation: 50, win: 150 },\n  diamond: { participation: 100, win: 300 },\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. **src/coinflip.ts - Coinflip Game Logic**\n\n**Program IDs:**\n```typescript\nexport const COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\n  \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"\n);\n\nexport const PROGRAM_IDS = {\n  COINFLIP: COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID,  // deprecated\n};\n```\n\n**PDA Derivation:**\n- `getMatchPda(creator: PublicKey)` - Seeds: `[\"match\", creator.toBytes()]`\n- `getConfigPda()` - Seeds: `[\"coinflip_config\"]`\n\n**Helper Functions:**\n```typescript\ngetEntryAmount(tier: Tier): number\n  → Returns TIER_AMOUNTS[tier]\n\ncalculatePotentialPayout(tier: Tier): number\n  → totalPool = entryAmount * 2\n  → fee = totalPool * 0.03\n  → returns totalPool - fee\n\ngetOppositeSide(side: CoinSide): CoinSide\n  → \"heads\" ↔ \"tails\"\n\ndetermineWinnerFromRandomness(randomness: Uint8Array, player1Side: CoinSide)\n  → Uses first byte % 2 (0 = heads, 1 = tails)\n  → Returns { result, player1Wins }\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **src/RoundStateMachine.ts - State Management**\n\nRound phases: `\"waiting\" | \"betting\" | \"active\" | \"resolving\" | \"complete\"`\n\nMethods:\n- `openBetting()` - waiting → betting\n- `closeBetting()` - betting → active\n- `startResolving()` - active → resolving\n- `complete()` - resolving → complete\n- `addPlayer(amount)` - updates player count & pool total\n- `subscribe(handler)` - listener pattern for state changes\n\n---\n\n### 8. **src/GameEventEmitter.ts - Event System**\n\nEvent types:\n```typescript\n\"round:created\" | \"round:betting_open\" | \"round:betting_closed\" | \n\"round:started\" | \"round:resolved\" | \"player:joined\" | \n\"player:cashed_out\" | \"state:updated\"\n```\n\nMethods: `on()`, `off()`, `emit()` - standard pub/sub with wildcard support\n\n---\n\n### 9. **src/payouts.ts - Payout Calculations**\n\n```typescript\ncalculatePariMutuelPayout(playerBet, winningPool, totalPool, feeBps = 300)\n  → feeMultiplier = 1 - feeBps / 10000\n  → poolAfterFees = totalPool * feeMultiplier\n  → playerShare = playerBet / winningPool\n  → returns poolAfterFees * playerShare\n\ncalculateWinnerPayout(totalPool, feeBps = 300)\n  → returns totalPool * (1 - feeBps / 10000)\n\nverifyPayoutInvariant(payouts, fees, totalPool, tolerance = 0.000001)\n  → Checks: sum(payouts) + fees ≈ totalPool\n```\n\n**NOTE:** All marked as UI-verification only; on-chain is authoritative.\n\n---\n\n### 10. **src/instructions.ts - Legacy Instruction Builders**\n\nPlaceholder instruction builders (deprecated):\n- `buildEntryInstruction(params)` - marked as placeholder\n- `buildCashoutInstruction(params)` - marked as placeholder\n\nUses a placeholder `POOL_MANAGER_PROGRAM_ID` - not for production use.\n\n---\n\n### 11. **src/browser.ts - Browser-Safe Exports**\n\nExports the same as index.ts **except**:\n- NO `buildEntryInstruction`, `buildCashoutInstruction` (Buffer-dependent)\n- NO raw `PROGRAM_IDS` (only type exports)\n\nIntended for client-side apps that don't need blockchain instruction construction.\n\n---\n\n## Summary - Key Patterns\n\n1. **Program IDs** are hardcoded constants (e.g., `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID`)\n2. **PDAs** use `PublicKey.findProgramAddressSync()` with specific seed patterns\n3. **Tier system** ties amounts to gameplay (0.005 SOL for iron → 1.0 SOL for diamond)\n4. **Fees** are baked into constants (300 bps total split 200/70/30)\n5. **Types** are centralized in `types.ts` with discriminated union phases\n6. **UI calculations** (payouts, state) are verification-only; on-chain is authoritative\n7. **Coinflip randomness** uses first byte % 2 for deterministic winner determination\n8. **Export patterns** support both Node.js and browser via conditional exports"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a70e4a1 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 39437\ntool_uses: 13\nduration_ms: 33008</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d859bc11-91b4-4b69-a88e-12eb400e4b26","uuid":"3610bdc1-c5e2-4133-907a-52b9c61df718","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the game-engine package at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/`. I need to understand:\n1. The